Destructor of JSON `Object` results in stack overflow when deeply O(100K) nested objects are present.

### Details
Construction of deeply nested JSON from a string succeeds via [loadFromString](https://github.com/envoyproxy/envoy/blob/099a9d71ebfd8aa9f823e1738b34138cb634a07b/source/common/json/json_loader.h#L21) but then is guaranteed to create a stack overflow due to destructor recursion:

```
